          <title>
            <string language="sl">Visoke Tatre</string>
            <string language="en">High Tatras</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Hohes Tatras</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Haut Tatras</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Tatras Elevado</string>

            <string language="x-mt-es">Tatras Alto</string>
          </title>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <description>
            <string language="sl">Nebo je rdeče zažarelo v jutranji zarji. To je začek novega dneva v visokih Tatrah - najvišje gorovje na Slovaškem.</string>
            <string language="en">The sky is illuminated by the rose-colored dawn. It is the birth of new day in High Tatras - the highest mountains in Slovakia.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">jutro</string>
            <string language="en">morning</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>

          </keyword>

          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Der Himmel wird durch die steigen-farbige 
Dämmerung belichtet. Es ist die Geburt des neuen Tages in hohem
Tatras - die höchsten Berge in Slowakei.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Le ciel est illuminé par l'aube lever-colorée. 
C'est la naissance du nouveau jour dans haut Tatras - les plus 
hautes montagnes en Slovaquie.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">O céu é iluminado pelo alvorecer 
levant-colorido. É o nascimento do dia novo em Tatras elevado -
as montanhas as mais elevadas em Slovakia.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Il cielo è illuminato dall'alba 
aumentare-colorata. È la nascita di nuovo giorno in alto Tatras
- le più alte montagne in Slovacchia.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ο ουρανός φωτίζεται μέχρι τη ροδαλός-χρωματισμένη 
αυγή. Είναι η γέννηση της νέας ημέρας σε υψηλό Tatras -
τα υψηλότερα βουνά στη Σλοβακία.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El cielo es iluminado por el amanecer 
levantar-coloreado. Es el nacimiento del nuevo día en Tatras 
alto - las montañas más altas de Eslovaquia.</string>
          </description>
